aa(lp48
VSo here's the thing.
p49
aVWe have a situation where private companies
p50
aVare applying censorship standards
p51
aVthat are often quite arbitrary
p52
aVand generally more narrow
p53
aVthan the free speech constitutional standards
p54
aVthat we have in democracies.
